[seufzt]

28:43.083 --> 28:44.458
[normale Stimme] Ja?

28:44.541 --> 28:45.791
High Five?

28:45.875 --> 28:48.500
Los geht's! Lasst uns feiern!

28:48.583 --> 28:50.166
